                    Created September 2023 for the UC Berkley Full Stack Web Development Bootcamp
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="footer-copyright">
                <div class="container">
                ¬© 2023 Tech Blog-O-Sphere
                <a class="purple-text text-lighten-4 right" href="#" target="_top">Top</a>
                </div>
            </section>
      </footer>
